## Banned Words

Avoid the following words. Use the preferred alternatives instead.

| Avoid | Use instead |
|-------|-------------|
| via | through, using, with, by, over |
| right (when meaning correct) | correct |

### Examples

❌ Connect to the database via the driver.
✅ Connect to the database using the driver.

❌ Send data via the API.
✅ Send data through the API.
